Item` 与 `GetCart` 等关键操作中尤其明显。以下是验证的结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"latency_spike\", \"cartservice->redis\", \"slow_response\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis 的响应显著延迟影响了 CartService 的操作\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常期间 Redis 操作如 HMSET 和 HGET 的异常平均耗时均超过正常水平的约 5 倍，使 CartService 的操作受阻\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**结论**: 数据支持根因假设为 `Redis` 的性能瓶颈导致了 CartService 的操作延迟。", "log_analysis_findings": "Based on the log analysis tool results, here is the synthesized data with relevant expert detection:\n\n### Log Analysis\nThe provided error logs indicate issues primarily related to the `adservice`. Here are the key findings:\n\n1. **Service Identified**: \n   - `service_name`: `adservice`\n   - `pod_name`: `adservice-2`\n   - `node_name`: `aiops-k8s-08`\n\n2. **Detected Log Keywords**:\n   - `adservice--gc`\n   - `java.lang.Exception`\n   - `InvocationTargetException`\n   - `GCHelper`\n\n3. **Key Log Messages**:\n   - \"Rule.execute called for AdService--gc\"\n   - \"AdService--gc execute\"\n   - \"Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\"\n   - \"Exception in thread \\\"Attach Listener\\\" java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\"\n   - \"Agent failed to start!\"\n   - \"calling installed(AdService--gc) for helper class org.chaos_mesh.byteman.helper.GCHelper\"\n\n### Hypothesis Verification\n\n**Hypothesis**: '(等待写入...)'\n\n#### Analysis:\n- **Errors Detected**: Multiple errors related to `AdService--gc` and `Byteman` agent invocation failures.\n- **Root Cause Indicators**:\n  - Frequent invocation of `GCHelper` and `Byteman` agent failures indicate stress or misconfiguration related to garbage collection processes.\n  - The recurring error \"attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\" suggests multiple failures due to improper initialization or repeated loading of components.\n\nBased on these logs, the root cause appears to 